        private void initialize_physicalstuff​(java.lang.String physicalstuff_type,
                                      int speed_obstacle,
                                      int xpos,
                                      int ypos,
                                      int w,
                                      int h,
                                      java.lang.String s)
        This is a factory design pattern that initialize different game elements
        参数:
        physicalstuff_type - the type(name) of the elements(belong to physical stuff)
        speed_obstacle - the speed
        xpos - xpos
        ypos - ypos
        w - width
        h - height
        s - picture path
